abstract: >
  A PowerShell toolkit to sync, install, and manage GitHub Copilot agents,
  instructions, hooks, skills, and workflows from the awesome-copilot community
  catalogue into VS Code. Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux via PowerShell 7+.
